{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, AI technology presents important opportunities in areas like improving nuclear safety, efficient risk management, and decision-making support.",
    "Such opportunities can maximize the positive changes AI can bring to the nuclear industry and facilitate the modernization of the IAEA regulatory framework.",
    "The study balances these challenges and opportunities in an unbiased manner, providing substantive direction on the effective application and evolution of AI regulation.",
    "Based on the research findings, I propose some practical recommendations for policymakers and practitioners in AI technology regulation.",
    "First, flexible approaches tailored to the rapid pace of technological progress are needed in AI regulation."
  ]
}